
Ques 03: Delivery Charge Calculation System

Project Overview
----------------
Develop a Spring Core application to calculate delivery charges using different delivery strategies.

Requirements

The application should support the following strategies with different charges:

Standard Delivery — ₹50 charge
Express Delivery — ₹100 charge
Same-Day Delivery — ₹200 charge

Charges should be calculated based on the delivery option selected.

Flow
User selects delivery type
Corresponding strategy calculates charges
Final delivery cost is displayed
